  <brief_title>The Efficacy of Permethrin 5%, Fusidic Acid 1% and Synthomycine 5% for Demodex - Blepharitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Efficacy Of Lyclear (Permethrin 5%) Vs Fusidic Acid1% and Synthomycine 5% for Demodex -Blepharitis Treatment, Prospective-Randomized Trial.</official_title>
